node.text:
‘Blue Lotus’
A masterpiece that will one day end up being viewed behind glass in a museum 🌟
100% designed and handmade by @serjewelry featuring Turquose and Amethyst with VVS Diamonds
(Sold) @thecrowncollection 👑 
_
The Blue Lotus was a psychedelic aphrodisiac used by the ancient Egyptians, and the leaves were found on King Tut
